-- Ayen Gains on Wind Turbines for Power Generation in Turkey
-- B y   B e n j a m i n   H a r v e y
-- 2012-03-19T16:13:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-19/ayen-gains-as-uses-wind-turbines-for-power-generation-in-turkey.html
Ayen Enerji AS (AYEN) , a Turkish utility,
rose to the highest level since November after saying it started
power generation using wind turbines.  The shares gained 2 percent to 1.53 liras at the close in
Istanbul, the highest since Nov. 17.  Ayen started production using half of the 36 turbines at
its 72-megawatt facility at Kayseri province in central  Turkey ,
the company said today in a statement to the  Istanbul Stock
Exchange .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Benjamin Harvey in Istanbul at 
